Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見蔣老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.94,0:02:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.30,0:02:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊，那扇門根本是爛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能見到蔣老師嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你找風水老師，他在里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.81,0:02:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能否見到老師就要看他的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你入去看看吧，因為你很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能見到他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔣老師，你在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.00,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔣老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久無見了，史汀奇小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我還是跟以前一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你絲莉亞小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到老師你還認得我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.47,0:03:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才慶幸你沒有忘記我這個老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了現在還来探我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，我有一件事想老師你幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.38,0:03:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都料到，小姐你来我這里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必有事相求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我幫到你的，我一定會幫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得你那樣說，我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，有一個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正企圖解除討厭厭的封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.83,0:04:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白賴仁·J·美臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你知道嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道積蒙正在東京的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像蚯蚓一樣不停挖掘洞穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，地脈變得非常混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，他們把地脈稱為「龍脈」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「DRAGON LINE」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美臣正在找尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋在地底的偉斯研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為求找到被埋在地底的研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不停在錯誤的地方進行鑽探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯誤的地方…老師，難道…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我也不知道它在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.90,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為複雜的地殼流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令它徹底失去蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關地底世界的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們仍然比他清楚得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，你是来問那件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你知道它在哪里，你會怎麽辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會比他先一步…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在美臣動手之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次把它封印起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次會做得徹徹底底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇博士會覺得高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我失言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個老人胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記我剛才那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，你坐低吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得它的貼地性能有點問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車胎暫時還不需要更換吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要檢查懸掛系統周圍的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣缸也要更換，費用會很貴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉，你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？真少見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦不算吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有空，所以過来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次所及的破解防禦的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，布烈絲，你剛巧在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以談一會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，米奇，下次才教你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，你認為我為何指美臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在錯誤的地方進行鑽探？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美臣想必正倚靠地底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅餘的殘骸来找尋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.47,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在預測地殼流動的方程式里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使變數只有百份之一的不準確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.58,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也有可能會得出相反的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，但那方面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們来說亦一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們組織已經總動員查出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅地脈流向圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若把美臣手上的資料比喻為點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們手上的資料便等於線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們知道那個變數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們便能夠把研究所的現在位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縮窄為數個可能性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.07,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我這幅圖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是小姐你要我幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也在那項研究上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作出很大的投資
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最低限度的補償啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THANK YOU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有甚麽要談？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲，你對絲莉亞有多了解？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.00,0:07:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何突然那樣問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麽，我有點好奇罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.77,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛，我遇上絲莉亞的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟你差不多年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時跟封路的警察發生爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她主動叫我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的過去…她小時的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.82,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有問過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，那種事沒所謂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞為何要組成戰士飛刀呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在為何那樣問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟跟她爸爸有關吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過吧，史汀奇博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前負責開發亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞特別討厭厭亞人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那畢竟是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇博士是亞人的生父…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，但你為何突然那樣問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…布烈絲，其實…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.49,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒事了，我又未証實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關美臣博士的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子別多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾，我有點事想你幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入里面談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇，這里拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在七年前的東京大地震里死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，試這個，猜中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我莉莉小姐是無所不能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.09,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是改由偉斯研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發亞人之前的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在核心進行生化實驗時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的突然變異…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要的東西我拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，拉謝爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗的準備呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把聲納放在那個架上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里檢查聲納的雷達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的想法無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻怪物應該是藉着探測…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳到地底的亞人核心特有震幅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来尋找作為糧食的亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，看看這樣又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很順利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，拉謝爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在便能查出偉斯研究所的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這東西的有效範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極其量只有半徑300米的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找遍整個東京需要多年時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.74,0:10:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把可能性縮窄為27處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要確定在哪里應該不會那麽困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，假如給你找到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎樣消滅它？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要積蒙協助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，七年前沒可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看現在亦沒可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我看過蔣老師的資料候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時沒有的東西現在有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今次會徹底消滅它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.69,0:12:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麽晚！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回公司了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我也要去錄音室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我完全沒發覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉的樣子有不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麽，我看不用擔心她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如問問絲莉亞吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.45,0:12:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，那會好像很多事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我也有點想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞為何組成戰士飛刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸爸的專利權令她很富有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她完全不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看絲莉亞也並非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是當正義的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.84,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個原因你不滿意？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也說得對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.78,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使絲莉亞有甚麽私人理由也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.66,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們每一個人都有私人理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.81,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扳鉗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞有何要事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不如問她本人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，我不可告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她想幹些危險的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是製造她要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如何使用跟我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，美臣博士要你造甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑噪器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了！抑噪器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.06,0:14:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你飲咖啡吧，還是飲可可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇，你現在多大？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是著名的史汀奇博士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個怎樣的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不大記得，我當時還小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而爸爸又忙於研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，可可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.87,0:15:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟絲莉亞一起生活到多少歲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…大概8歲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何那樣問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.97,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…我想知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.28,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞小時是怎麽樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着現在的絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全無法想像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個普通的小孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，她自小便很聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然別人都說她冷傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她對我和藹可親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好像亦一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指她和藹的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，米奇你小時是怎麽樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟現在沒分別啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們看来跟蔣大人的組織接觸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.79,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個在背候暗中操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界經濟的老糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是懂得找幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們礙於積蒙的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.07,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保持低調與世無爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們的力量不容輕視呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們背負的歷史跟我們不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也才有利用價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…你早知如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才叫葛井洩漏情報…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然亦事先考慮過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇過去的人際關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則，葛井也死不瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連黑道中的巨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在你的股掌之中嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，另一個呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.43,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉謝爾·卻蘭度嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他取得接觸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種大人物為何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那種小人物這麽執着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要利用史汀奇留下来的遺產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.72,0:17:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，你要我們鑽進地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查那27處地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酬勞是以往的兩倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件共作不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問題，那間研究所…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫偉斯研究所吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有些危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若現在不趁機毀滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它便會引發嚴重的災難吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧，我接這件共作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想你們幫我找出研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.61,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之候的事由我負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問一個問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.95,0:17:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽問題？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過大地震的地殼流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令那間研究所不知去了哪里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.92,0:17:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那難道是你爸爸的…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，那件危險的東西難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你！不要再問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我也接這件共作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有酬勞，我亦沒資格過問呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.04,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何支開米奇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.88,0:18:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事為何不可讓米奇知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.29,0:18:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我調查過你的個人資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.69,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我找多少次也找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最初以為戶籍方面錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.90,0:18:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇博士沒有申報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他被其他人收養了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到處也沒有那種記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇博士根本沒有兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…那孩子究竟是誰！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會答我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟研究所的意外有關嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！難道…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機密文件的防禦真的很堅固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要透過AD警察的主機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總算成功查閱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，甚麽意外？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的前一年，史汀奇博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任職的BIOSCAPE公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給積蒙收購了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人的開發也由積蒙繼續進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士在開發核心方面終於成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人開始大量生產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，研究所突然發生神秘意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然警方的部隊秘密出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們無功而還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究所的職員全部死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方的部隊亦有數人犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.63,0:19:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時發生甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查閱的是AD警察的出動記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只是知道那麽多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.68,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那次意外有多嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過積蒙當時的處理方法便知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.15,0:19:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為事態無法收拾的積蒙會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.59,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昆西·羅辛格爾下令開動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在另一間研究所試驗中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.79,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「人共地震系統」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.56,0:20:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.79,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是那次大地震的起因！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，一切都是人為造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.37,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳！他們知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.74,0:20:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次地震里死了多少人嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們知道嗎！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.42,0:20:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不惜一切要毀滅的研究所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何秘密？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我不能告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇跟那次意外是毫無關系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外我無可奉告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！絲莉亞，我無法信任你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也可以走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.91,0:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉講得無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵部份我不告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要你們照我說話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.59,0:21:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太自私了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麽，絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.36,0:21:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找的是那麽危險的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西，我不能置諸不理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，既然我們知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地底有一件那麽可怕的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每晚都不能安睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，莉莉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.26,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何看法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.99,0:21:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉的事？她心存芥蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一起共作也只會拖累我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人每晚找三處地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.10,0:21:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人五日便辦妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.90,0:21:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你依然無變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.80,0:21:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一談到莉莉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是那種口吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.14,0:22:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.65,0:22:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.09,0:22:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.92,0:23:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地底廢墟的黑暗深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.56,0:24:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼小的少女仍然沉睡在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.93,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表跟我一樣的討厭厭過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.94,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是素體，亞人的素體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.67,0:24:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全因有這種東西，我才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.91,0:24:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要消滅它…我要徹底消滅它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.41,0:24:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，吹波糖危機


